  <phrase title="option_explain.aiconnect_translation_provider" version_id="1012900" version_string="1.1.29"><![CDATA[Choose how translation works for AI agents connected to your forum.<br><br><b>AI Self-Translate</b> — The AI agent translates content using its own language abilities. No external API, no limits, best quality. <em>Recommended.</em><br><b>MyMemory API</b> — Uses the free <a href="https://mymemory.translated.net/" target="_blank">MyMemory</a> translation service. Limited to ~5,000 characters/day.<br><b>Disabled</b> — No translation capability offered to AI agents.]]></phrase>
